49:45.525 --> 49:47.902
Was it good? I couldn't tell.
I moved a lot.

49:47.944 --> 49:49.404
Was that bad?
Did they hate me?

49:49.445 --> 49:50.988
It was good.
They loved you.

49:51.030 --> 49:52.907
Sal looked mad when I went over
to the phone bank.

49:52.949 --> 49:54.325
Did it work?
Could you hear me?

49:54.367 --> 49:55.827
Trust me, it was great.

49:55.868 --> 49:57.662
It was almost better
that I went on later.

49:57.704 --> 49:59.664
The circumstances were bad,
but the pressure was off.

49:59.706 --> 50:02.208
